    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Anno 1122 die 3 Febr. Ind. XV. Reverend. <persName key="#Bishops #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3547">Vilanus</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Bishops #Canons" ref="#juridical_persons/1425"><rs
                                key="#Bishops">episc.</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Bishops #Canons" ref="#places/9"
                            >Brix.</placeName></orgName> consilio et consensu <rs key="#Canons"
                            >Canonicorum</rs>, et <persName key="#Archpriests #Witness"><name
                                ref="Lanzus">Lanzonis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archpriests">Archipresbiteri</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">eccl.</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Archpriests" ref="#juridical_persons/2005">S.
                            Mariae</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Churches #Archpriests #Cells/hermitages" ref="#places/2475"
                            >Medula</placeName> promisit se suosque successores adversus <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Priors #Monks #Missus #Cells/hermitages #Landed_possessions #Abbots"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001"><rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >Monas.</rs></orgName> non posse causare de <rs key="#Cells/hermitages"
                            >Capella</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Cells/hermitages" ref="#juridical_persons/2066">S.
                            Viti</orgName> et de omnibus rebus possessis a Monasterio quae
                        dicebantur pertinere Eccl.ae <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2004">S. Justi</orgName>. Ipse vicem se accipit
                        cum Lanzone suprad. a Mon. per Reverendum <persName key="#Priors"
                            ref="#people/3509">Ubertum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">Priorem</rs>, et <persName key="#Monks"><name
                                ref="Heinricum">Enricum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachum</rs>, et <persName key="#Monks #Missus"><name
                                ref="Giselbertus">Gilbertum</name></persName> monachum <rs
                            key="#Missus">missus</rs> Mon. Capellam S. Justi cum <rs key="#Size">sex
                            iug.</rs>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terrae</rs>. Haec conventio facta est D.no
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3538">Pontio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">Abb.</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2091">Cluniac.</orgName> et
                        R.mo <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3549">Enrico</persName> Abbate
                            <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2410"
                            >angeliacensi</orgName>, mediantibus consensu Abbatis suprad.ti Monast.
                        spirituali reverentia <orgName
                            key="#Bishops #Canons #Cells/hermitages #Landed_possessions #Mother_churches #Deacons #Subdeacons #Priests"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1425">Eccl. Brix.</orgName> servata. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Subscripsi</rs> ego <persName key="#Witness #Deacons"
                                ><name ref="Lanfrancus">Lanfrancus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">Diaconus</rs> maioris Ecclesiae. Item <persName
                            key="#Witness #Deacons"><name ref="Lanfrancus"
                            >Lanfrancus</name></persName> Diaconus maioris Ecclesiae. Item <persName
                            key="#Witness #Deacons"><name ref="Lanfrancus"
                            >Lanfrancus</name></persName> eiusdem Ecclesiae Diaconus. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Subdeacons"><name ref="Hubertus"
                            >Ubertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">Subdic.</rs> ss. <persName key="#Witness #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Gezo">Gezzo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">Praesb.</rs> ss. Ego <persName key="#Witness #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Villanus">Villanus</name></persName> Praesb. ss. Ego
                        Lanzo Archipraesb. Medul. Ecclesiae laudo et confirmo. Ego Villanus Dei
                        gratia Brixiensis Ecclesiae Episcopus huius operis facta confirmavi. Ego
                            <persName ref="#people/3548" key="#Witness #Bishops"
                            >Manfredus</persName> Dei gratia Brixiensis Ecclesiae Episcopus ss. et
                        confirmavi. Ego <persName key="#Witness #Subdeacons"><name ref="Paulus"
                                >Paulus</name></persName> Brix. Eccl. Subdiac. ss. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Subdeacons"><name ref="Oddo">Oddo</name></persName>
                        eiusdem Eccl. Subdiac. ss. Ego <persName key="#Witness #Subdeacons"><name
                                ref="Albertus">Albertus</name></persName> eiusdem Eccl. Subdiac. ss.
                        Ibi fuere <persName key="#Witness #Advocatus"><name ref="Oddo"
                            >Oddo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">Advocatus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Huguccio/de Martinengo">Ugucionus de
                            Martinengo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Obizo/della Porta">Obizo della Porta</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Lanfrancus/Zinzala">Lanfrancus
                                Zinzala</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Lanzus/Bergomensis">Lanzo Bergomensis</name></persName> et
                        reliqui plures. Ego <persName key="#Witness #Canons"><name ref="Philippus"
                                >Filippus</name></persName> Brixiensis Ecclesiae Canonicus ss. Ego
                            <persName key="#Witness #Deacons"><name ref="Aldus"
                            >Aldo</name></persName> eiusdem Ecclesiae Diaconus ss. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Subdeacons"><name ref="Oprandus"
                            >Oprandus</name></persName> maior. Eccl. Sudd. ss. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Subdeacons"><name ref="Benedictus"
                            >Benedictus</name></persName> Ecclesiae <orgName key="#Subdeacons"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2411">S. Petri in Oliveto</orgName> Subdiaconus
                        ss. Ego <persName key="#Notary #Judge #Breve/memoratorium #Writer"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/notarius">Ioannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">Notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">Judex</rs> interfui et
                        hoc <rs key="#Breve/memoratorium">Breve</rs> rogatus <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
